// src/messages.js
export const messages = [
  {
    "id": 1,
    "sender": "Alice",
    "receiver": "You",
    "profilePicture": "https://via.placeholder.com/50",
    "message": "Hey! How are you doing?",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-21T10:30:00"
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "sender": "You",
    "receiver": "Bob",
    "profilePicture": "https://via.placeholder.com/50",
    "message": "I'm doing great, thanks! How about you?",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-21T10:32:00"
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "sender": "Charlie",
    "receiver": "You",
    "profilePicture": "https://via.placeholder.com/50",
    "message": "Don't forget about the meeting later.",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-21T10:35:00"
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "sender": "You",
    "receiver": "Alice",
    "profilePicture": "https://via.placeholder.com/50",
    "message": "Thanks for the reminder! See you there.",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-21T10:36:00"
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "sender": "Bob",
    "receiver": "You",
    "profilePicture": "https://via.placeholder.com/50",
    "message": "Let’s grab lunch after the meeting?",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-21T10:37:00"
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "sender": "You",
    "receiver": "Charlie",
    "profilePicture": "https://via.placeholder.com/50",
    "message": "Sounds good! Let’s catch up after.",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-21T10:40:00"
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "sender": "Alice",
    "receiver": "You",
    "profilePicture": "https://via.placeholder.com/50",
    "message": "Have you finished that report yet?",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-21T11:00:00"
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "sender": "You",
    "receiver": "Bob",
    "profilePicture": "https://via.placeholder.com/50",
    "message": "Yes, just submitted it!",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-21T11:02:00"
  }
];
